summary: An Ordinance transferring the sum of one and 80/100 ($1.80) dollars from Local Improvement District No. 1541 Fund, created by Ordinance No. 16698, providing for the improvement of Alley in Block 10, Boren & Denny's Addition to the City of Seattle, by constructing sewers and laying water mains therein, into the General Fund on account of the deficiency in the Fixed Estimate of said District.
